# Exact — environment
#
# Exact is fully static and runs entirely in the browser. It needs NO server-side
# secrets to build, host, or run — there is intentionally nothing to configure here.
#
# The optional AI features (photo reading now; plain-English input & tutoring next)
# use bring-your-own-key: the visitor pastes their own Anthropic API key, which is
# stored only in their browser (localStorage) and sent only to api.anthropic.com.
# No key ever lives on a server or in this repo.
